{"tid":137866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持台灣自治 美前駐聯大使：川普應重談一中","createTime":"2017-02-28T06:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T17:31:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e346114bca3c5a0422eb4be0745a23b6920dde4","tid":137866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpsZW15F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpsZW15F.jpg&h=3386473c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">美國前駐聯合國大使波頓表示，川普政府應重新透過協商，改變40年來美國的「一中政策」慣例。（路透資料照）</span><br />\n2017-02-28  07:15<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國前駐聯合國大使波頓（John Bolton）接受媒體訪問時表示，敦促美國總統川普（Donald Trump）應該顛覆美國40年來的慣例，重新協商「一中政策」。波頓說，「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我們支持台灣人，支持他們持續的自治，獨立於中國之外。</strong></span>」<br />\n根據華盛頓自由燈塔網站（Washington Free Beacon）27日報導，波頓表示，「一中政策」是1972年美國總統尼克森（Richard Nixon）訪問中國期間所設立，已缺乏歷史觀點，並不能反映在目前東亞地區的情勢。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>波頓說，台灣現在絕大多數的當地人認為自己是「台灣人」，而非「中國人」。</strong></span><br />\n波頓說，「一中政策」是模棱兩可的，北京與華盛頓有不同的解讀方式。北京認為，「一中政策」指中國人民共和國是唯一合法的政府，並且包括台灣。但華府卻認為，從上海公報中明確表示只有一個中國，但沒有否認台灣的主權。<br />\n波頓表示，若是美國、台灣和中國能夠釐清彼此關係，將大有幫助，而非琢磨「一中政策」4個字意涵，沒有任何意義。他早前向保守政治行動會議（CPAC）支持者公開表態，川普政府必需清楚說明，台灣民眾若沒有一面倒的同意，中國和台灣絕對不會統一。<br />\n波頓預測，中國將是21世紀美國最重要的戰略問題，川普應該立即要求中國從南海和東海撤出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1988372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1988372&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=3f31a90b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1988372&h=b3ad0cde\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1988372</a>"},{"pid":"09c2c5dbb129b53db8f8a7aad8239fe4e48caf88","tid":137866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaac393babb93376fb23416e1782508b5fbf9b57","tid":137866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf39f634690af104186f1fad424449c53f8f7ee","tid":137866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c405df45a6451f5563fe98e45fd1246351785642","tid":137866,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"美聯中令蘇聯解體後<br />\n係時候檢討一中政策"},{"pid":"9027cfbf7285df54eb01190d30b848f965af1a0f","tid":137866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102399bc4b000c8eea64b9e4bcf682c9c694fcd1","tid":137866,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"呢條友出名親台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c88df0245ef1dfd98ecc64d0995be706e002cff","tid":137866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}